OOC: Naga should see the warp by now.

The Night Star advanced in the void of space. The Tripredacus ship was 
near to the point where the two previous ships had disappeared.

Tyrael: Strikers, somewhere around here, two ships were lost on 
sensors. One of them is the Predacon ship. Everyone to their station. 
Shadow Star, man the cannons. Talon you get the pilot's seat. Naga, 
signal anything you cath on sensors and raise the shield at maximum 
available power.
